00:01:06.120 --> 00:01:10.920
 And now, so therefore, again, this motivation is so important.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:13.920
 And motivation is really the turning point.

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:19.580
 Motivation is like just the key point, key point.

00:01:19.580 --> 00:01:23.160
 And therefore, this kind of igniting all the goodness

00:01:23.160 --> 00:01:27.040
 thought and goodness intention always

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:31.480
 is so important because that is not just important.

00:01:31.480 --> 00:01:33.240
 It's self is practice.

00:01:33.240 --> 00:01:37.400
 That is heart of the practices, essence of the practices.

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:40.560
 And we're talking about the hundo, the beginner preparations

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:42.280
 or the foundation practices.

00:01:42.280 --> 00:01:43.000
 What's it?

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:47.240
 In the always teaching said, bring more joy, more appreciation,

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:50.200
 more kindness, compare your thoughts for all the living

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:52.080
 beings, more bodhic than that thought.

00:01:52.080 --> 00:01:56.600
 Also reflecting all this kind of situation and circumstances,

00:01:56.600 --> 00:01:59.760
 no more preciousness, more kind of happy,

00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:02.160
 more appreciative of these things.

00:02:02.160 --> 00:02:05.160
 And the same kind where we are, what we are,

00:02:05.160 --> 00:02:08.640
 is also not this permanent, it's this kind of reflecting

00:02:08.640 --> 00:02:12.800
 truly as it is where things are and kind of softening

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:14.600
 our grasping and clinging.

00:02:14.600 --> 00:02:18.240
 Because grasping and clinging is regimented, is diluted.

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:19.840
 It is not natural.

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:22.080
 And there's a hindrance, obstacles,

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:24.440
 order to kind of like pre-that.

00:02:24.440 --> 00:02:27.960
 Again, we have to use the same remedy and the thought

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:30.520
 as like homopedic things.

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:32.880
 That mind created things, we have

00:02:32.880 --> 00:02:34.920
 to use the mind's techniques.

00:02:34.920 --> 00:02:36.800
 Love and kind is a comparison.

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:39.840
 It's the homopedic, in a way, techniques

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:43.640
 to remove the ego and all this negative emotion, which

00:02:43.640 --> 00:02:45.640
 is created by the mind itself.

00:02:45.640 --> 00:02:47.720
 So therefore, all this teaching said

00:02:47.720 --> 00:02:51.040
 how much important in the teaching at the foundation.

00:02:51.040 --> 00:02:53.240
 And then also principle body of the practice,

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:56.520
 again, maintaining the same, that motivation,

00:02:56.520 --> 00:02:58.600
 the mundo of the foundation practices,

00:02:58.600 --> 00:03:02.240
 but then more strong, more kind of continually,

00:03:02.240 --> 00:03:06.480
 of keeping that flame, that fire.

00:03:06.480 --> 00:03:09.440
 And that is known as then the main part of the body

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:10.600
 practices.

00:03:10.600 --> 00:03:15.440
 And then the result will be that as we started the foundation,

00:03:15.440 --> 00:03:18.640
 as we continue to maintain, when you discover that,

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:20.640
 is then the result in achievement.

00:03:20.640 --> 00:03:23.840
 Then, all that.

