00:04:30.680 --> 00:04:33.680
 And so therefore, this cause and condition

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:36.960
 looks like so sometimes insignificant.

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:41.880
 But however, the cause and condition is so important.

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:46.520
 Even the smallest things can bring a huge, big result,

00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:50.280
 whether that is negative, whether that is positive.

00:04:50.280 --> 00:04:52.840
 So therefore, being as the practitioners,

00:04:52.840 --> 00:04:56.400
 we're trying to really learn more kind of positive things

00:04:56.400 --> 00:05:01.560
 and trying to also avoid even the smallest negative actions.

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:05.280
 And that is then good for us, good for the others,

00:05:05.280 --> 00:05:09.120
 and good for our continued growth of the practice,

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:12.200
 or practice, or the dharma.

00:05:12.200 --> 00:05:15.160
 And for those reasons in the Buddha's teaching said,

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:18.000
 for example, like six parametas, when

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:21.320
 we do generous practices, of course, generous practice

00:05:21.320 --> 00:05:23.080
 is so important, so special.

00:05:23.080 --> 00:05:24.560
 Everybody knows that.

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:27.160
 But generous practice also brings

00:05:27.160 --> 00:05:30.560
 more abundance of luxuries in the teaching system,

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:34.200
 when you do the generous practices.

00:05:34.200 --> 00:05:36.640
 And then, when we do the morality practice,

00:05:36.640 --> 00:05:40.280
 the ethic practices, it will bring more always joy,

00:05:40.280 --> 00:05:44.160
 happiness, happiness, and particularly in the future,

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:45.520
 in the future lives.

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:48.880
 For example, generous practice make more reach.

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:51.440
 And the morality practice, we make

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:55.440
 us to take bone in higher realms, always.

00:05:55.440 --> 00:05:57.920
 And the patient tolerance practices,

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:59.840
 it makes ourselves more--

00:05:59.840 --> 00:06:02.440
 also in the future, it makes more beautiful.

00:06:02.440 --> 00:06:06.560
 Or in the future lives, it makes physical very beautiful,

00:06:06.560 --> 00:06:09.320
 the morality, the patient practices.

00:06:09.320 --> 00:06:10.880
 And the joy of our practices will

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:14.560
 make kind of very dominating in the future lives,

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:15.680
 in the teaching set.

00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:18.120
 It will bring more dominating, more kind

00:06:18.120 --> 00:06:20.120
 of powerful persons, that.

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:23.440
 And then the concentration practice also

00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:28.320
 will bring in future result, as like very calm and peaceful,

00:06:28.320 --> 00:06:30.440
 more kind of peaceful state of mind.

00:06:30.440 --> 00:06:34.040
 And then wisdom will bring always wisdom, intelligence,

00:06:34.040 --> 00:06:37.520
 to our heart, mind, or the Buddhahood, finally.

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:41.120
 And of course, all of that finally brings the Buddhahood.

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:43.360
 So all the achievement--

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:47.000
 so those are the teaching often said.

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:50.920
 And therefore, again, we're trying to kind of do as much

00:06:50.920 --> 00:06:54.280
 as we can do those six part of mental practices.

00:06:54.280 --> 00:06:57.640
 Or even the smallest, the minimum kind of goodness activity

00:06:57.640 --> 00:06:59.440
 that we do.

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:02.720
 And then we could also really harp in the joy each time

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:04.440
 when we're able to do kind of--

00:07:04.440 --> 00:07:06.920
 igniting that joy and appreciation

00:07:06.920 --> 00:07:09.560
 at the same time, kind of like sit, in a way,

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:12.160
 kind of like sit forward, that may I

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:16.120
 be able to do this even more in a future kind of way,

00:07:16.120 --> 00:07:19.560
 inspiring one's own self, moving continuing the path

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:20.640
 and progress.

00:07:20.640 --> 00:07:24.400
 And that is really known as the practicing the dharma.

