00:08:00.560 --> 00:08:04.080
 And therefore, always be thoughtful is very important.

00:08:04.080 --> 00:08:08.240
 Thoughtful and start with the small, minimum.

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:12.600
 We're not going to looking always the big gigantic things

00:08:12.600 --> 00:08:13.680
 immediately.

00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:16.640
 But even the minimum, the smallest

00:08:16.640 --> 00:08:18.520
 is the relief foundation.

00:08:18.520 --> 00:08:20.680
 From there, everything started.

00:08:20.680 --> 00:08:23.440
 And therefore, kind of very thoughtful,

00:08:23.440 --> 00:08:28.280
 do the even smallest good activity that adds up

00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:29.880
 and that build up that.

00:08:29.880 --> 00:08:33.640
 And we're not going to wait for big things.

00:08:33.640 --> 00:08:36.080
 And big things that we can do, that's great.

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:40.880
 But do what we can do with joy, with appreciation.

00:08:40.880 --> 00:08:43.040
 And those are always in the teaching

00:08:43.040 --> 00:08:46.760
 said, which is very practical way.

